r.s: Provides extra data structures and iterable/array functionality.
r.d: teds (Tentative Extra Data Structures) is a collection of data structures and iterable functionality
r.n: * Add Teds\BitSet providing similar functionality to a Vector of booleans, using a single bit per boolean. * Fix stub documentation and qualify `\Iterator` for StableMinHeap/StableMaxHeap in documentation.
